FROM rgdb."DbT3070KogakuGassanJikoFutanGaku" AS "DbT3070KogakuGassanJikoFutanGaku" LEFT JOIN rgdb."DbV1001HihokenshaDaicho" AS "DbV1001HihokenshaDaicho" ON "DbV1001HihokenshaDaicho"."hihokenshaNo" = "DbT3070KogakuGassanJikoFutanGaku"."hihokenshaNo" LEFT JOIN rgua."UaFt200FindShikibetsuTaisho"('2',#{基準年月日},true,'DB',FALSE,'','','','','','','','','','','',true, '','','','','','','',true,'','','','','','','','','','','',true,true,true,true,true,true,true,true,true,true, true,'','','','','','','','',true,'','',true,true,true,'','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','{}') AS "ShikibetsuTaisho" ON "ShikibetsuTaisho"."shikibetsuCode" = "DbV1001HihokenshaDaicho"."shikibetsuCode" LEFT JOIN rgdb."DbT3071KogakuGassanJikoFutanGakuMeisai" AS "DbT3071KogakuGassanJikoFutanGakuMeisai" ON "DbT3071KogakuGassanJikoFutanGakuMeisai"."hihokenshaNo" = "DbT3070KogakuGassanJikoFutanGaku"."hihokenshaNo" AND "DbT3071KogakuGassanJikoFutanGakuMeisai"."taishoNendo" = "DbT3070KogakuGassanJikoFutanGaku"."taishoNendo" AND "DbT3071KogakuGassanJikoFutanGakuMeisai"."hokenshaNo" = "DbT3070KogakuGassanJikoFutanGaku"."hokenshaNo" AND "DbT3071KogakuGassanJikoFutanGakuMeisai"."shikyuShinseishoSeiriNo" = "DbT3070KogakuGassanJikoFutanGaku"."shikyuShinseishoSeiriNo" AND "DbT3071KogakuGassanJikoFutanGakuMeisai"."rirekiNo" = "DbT3070KogakuGassanJikoFutanGaku"."rirekiNo" AND "DbT3071KogakuGassanJikoFutanGakuMeisai"."isDeleted" = false WHERE "DbT3070KogakuGassanJikoFutanGaku"."kakunin_UketoriYM" = #{確認情報受取年月} AND ("DbT3070KogakuGassanJikoFutanGaku"."hoseiZumi_SofuYM" = '' OR "DbT3070KogakuGassanJikoFutanGaku"."hoseiZumi_SofuYM" IS NULL ) AND ("DbT3070KogakuGassanJikoFutanGaku"."realHoseiJissiYMD" = '' OR
